Information

"Kirarin☆Revolution Special Live" was a special concert featuring artists for the anime Kirarin☆Revolution. The DVD was filmed on November 9, 2008 at JCB Hall.

Members featured in this release

MilkyWay

Kusumi Koharu as Tsukishima Kirari

Kitahara Sayaka as Yukino Noel

Kikkawa Yuu as Hanasaki Cobeni

SHIPS

Ide Takuya as Kazama Hiroto

Kanai Shikou as Hiwatari Seiji
